Installation instructions:

Install DuckDescribe:
script/plugin install ...

Install Engines:
script/plugin install git://github.com/lazyatom/engines.git
require File.join(File.dirname(__FILE__), '../vendor/plugins/engines/boot')  after boot in environment.rb

Generate plugin migrations:
script/generate plugin_migration
rake db:migrate

Add Routing:
add "map.from_plugin :plugin_name" to your Routing

Require libxml in your environment.rb  
require 'xml/libxml'
